    <surface xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" lrx="5138" lry="7032" partOf="#ox-frankenstein_volume_ii" ulx="0" uly="0" mith:folio="40r" mith:shelfmark="MS. Abinger c. 57" xml:base="ox-ms_abinger_c57/ox-ms_abinger_c57-0079.xml" xml:id="ox-ms_abinger_c57-0079">
       <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ms_abinger_c57/ms_abinger_c57-0079.jp2"/>
       <zone rend="bordered" type="pagination"><line><unclear>101</unclear></line></zone>
       <zone type="main">
          <delSpan rend="vertical_line" spanTo="#c57-0079.01"/>
          <line>to my slavery.<add place="superlinear"><metamark>X</metamark></add>
             <del rend="strikethrough">But <unclear extent="1" unit="chars"/></del>
             <del rend="strikethrough">But</del>
             <mod>
                <del rend="strikethrough">could</del>
                <del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear">should</add></del>
             </mod> I <mod>
                <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add>
                <add place="superlinear">should</add>
             </mod> leave</line>
          <line><del rend="strikethrough">Geneva &amp; the fiend beli</del>
             <del rend="strikethrough">&amp;</del> my friends</line>
          <line>unconscious of the existence of their</line>
          <line>enemy &amp; unprotected from his attacks</line>
          <line>exasperated as he might be by my <w ana="start"/>depar</line>
          <line>ture<w ana="end"/> – But then he had promised to</line>
          <line>follow me every where &amp; might</line>
          <line>he not accompany me to England–the</line>
          <line>thought was dreadful in itself but</line>
          <line>soothing inasmuch as my friends would</line>
          <line>be in safety. <del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear"><metamark function="displacement" xml:id="c57-0079.02">X</metamark><zone corresp="#c57-0079.02" type="left_margin">
             <addSpan hand="#pbs" spanTo="#c57-0079.03"/>
             <line>the thought of</line>
             <line>the possibility<add><metamark function="sequence">5</metamark></add></line>
             <line>of the reverse</line>
             <line>must have</line>
             <line>been dreadful</line>
             <anchor xml:id="c57-0079.03"/>
          </zone></add></del> The thoughts
             occurred</line>
          <line>rapidly to me &amp; I answered my <w ana="start"/>fa</line>
          <line>ther<w ana="end"/> with eagerness that I should</line>
          <line>be delighted to visit <del instant="true" rend="strikethrough">Engl</del> England</line>
          <line>with Clerval and that <del rend="strikethrough">travel</del> the</line>
          <line>idea of travelling was inchanting to</line>
          <line>me.</line>
          <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
          <delSpan rend="vertical_line" spanTo="#c57-0079.04"/>
          <line rend="indent2">Your <del instant="true" rend="strikethrough">journey</del> travels, said
             my</line>
          <line>father, will occupy the space of</line>
          <line>two years– on your return you</line>
          <line><del rend="strikethrough">shall be united to your cousin</del></line>
          <anchor xml:id="c57-0079.04"/>
          <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
          <line rend="indent2">Our plan was soon arranged.</line>
          <line>I should travel to Strasburgh where</line>
          <line>Clerval would join me &amp; we</line>
          <line>should proceed down the Rhine</line>
          <line>together.<del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear"><unclear reason="illegible">tow</unclear></add></del> Some short time would</line>
          <line>be spent in the towns of Holland</line>
          <line>&amp; many months in England. We were</line>
          <line>to return by france &amp; it was <w ana="start"/>sup</line>
          <line>posed<w ana="end"/> that this tour would occupy</line>
          <line>the space of two years. My father</line>
          <line>pleased himself with the reflection</line>
          <line>that I should be united to <w ana="start"/>Eliza</line>
          <line>beth<w ana="end"/> immediately on my return</line>
          <anchor xml:id="c57-0079.01"/>
       </zone>
       <zone type="left_margin">
          <line><add><metamark function="sequence">3</metamark></add></line>
       </zone>
       
       <zone type="left_margin">
          <line><add><metamark>X</metamark></add></line>
       </zone>
       
       
       
       
